public class SetOps
extends java.lang.Object

Note: This code is based on - Java Tutorial: The Set Interface
Using LinkedHashSet, even though slightly slower than HashSet, in order to ensure order is always respected (i.e. if called with TreeSet or LinkedHashSet implementations).

Author:
Ciaran O'Reilly, Ravi Mohan
